# ===========================================================================
#  NEXUS_tapeout_connector — keep ONLY the Altium design source.
#  Tracked: *.PrjPcb, *.PrjPcbStructure, *.SchDoc, *.PcbDoc, *.SchLib,
#           *.PcbLib, *.BomDoc, and the Pin Manager CSVs
#           ("CNFET Processor PCB - *.csv"). Everything else is ignored.
# ===========================================================================

# --- Non-design material (datasheets, MCM, spreadsheets, analysis) ---
non-altium-files/

# --- Altium local history / generated outputs / logs ---
History/
__Previews/
__Preview/
Project Outputs*/
Project Logs*/

# --- Pin Manager scratch/export artifacts (the CSVs are kept, these aren't) ---
Pin Files/
*.PinInfo

# --- Specctra / external router session files ---
*.dsn
*.ses
*.do
*.cctpref
*.rte
*.w

# --- Reports, logs, messages ---
*.html
*.htm
*.Txt
*.DRC
*.LDP
*.Error
*.Logs
*.REP
*.csv.Annotation

# --- Temp / lock / user-layout files ---
*.Lock
*.~*
*.PcbDoc.Annotation
*.PcbDoc.DesignAnalysis
*.SchDoc.Annotation
*.Annotation
*.DAT
*.DXPPrj
*.OutJob.Annotation
~$*
desktop.ini
